headline: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) Unveils High-Performance Probes For Enhanced Semiconductor Efficiency Testing
summary: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) recently unveiled an advanced family of optically isolated differential probes tailored for GaN and SiC semiconductors, gaining industry attention at the APEC 2025. Despite this, the company's stock experienced a 1.9% decline over the past week. This price movement aligns with a broader market downturn, underscored by political and economic uncertainties stemming from the Trump administration's recent tariff announcements on Canadian imports, which...
